sion%20of%20diplomats%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20amid%20a%20deepening%20row%20over%20claims%20linking%20%26quot%3Bagents%20of%20the%20Indian%20government%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20killing%20of%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fhardeep-singh-nijjar%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20Canadian%20citizen%2C%20in%20June%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20-%20which%20has%20yet%20to%20respond%20to%20these%20latest%20comments%20-%20has%20set%20up%20a%20high-level%20committee%20to%20investigate%20the%20allegation.%20However%20New%20Delhi%20has%20repeatedly%20shot%20down%20%26quot%3Babsurd%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bmotivated%26quot%3B%20the%20claim%20it%20was%20linked%20to%20the%20murder%2C%20pointing%20out%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhardeep-singh-nijjar-killing-s-jaishankar-asks-canada-to-provide-evidence-4577831%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eno%20evidence%20has%20been%20provided%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0to%20back%20up%20the%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20Delhi%20also%20said%20that%20since%20the%20allegations%20were%20first%20made%2C%20the%20Trudeau%20administration%20%26quot%3Bhas%20not%20shared%20a%20shred%20of%20evidence%20with%20the%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20despite%20many%20requests...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20comments%20after%20India%20ejected%20six%20Canadian%20diplomats%20-%20including%20acting%20High%20Commissioner%20Stewart%20Wheeler%20and%20his%20deputy%20-%20Mr%20Trudeau%20said%20he%20had%20shared%20information%20about%20the%20accusations%20with%20Five%20Eyes%20partners%2C%20particularly%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20latest%20charges%2C%20though%2C%20represent%20an%20escalation%20as%20they%20allege%20a%20wider%20campaign%20of%20the%20Indian%20government%20-%20of%20working%2C%20Mr%20Trudeau%20said%2C%20with%20organised%20crime%20elements%20in%20Canada%20to%20%26quot%3Bcollect%20-%20through%20questionable%20and%20illegal%20means%20-%20information%20on%20Canadian%20citizens...%20(that%20is%20fed%20to%20criminal%20organisations)%20that%20would%20then%20take%20violent%20actions%20from%20extortion%20to%20murder%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it%20is%20obvious%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20made%20a%20fundamental%20error%20in%20thinking%20they%20could%20engage%20in%20supporting%20criminal%20activity%20against%20Canadians%2C%20here%20on%20Canadian%20soil.%20Whether%20it%20be%20murders%20or%20extortion%20or%20other%20violent%20acts%2C%20it%20is%20absolutely%20unacceptable%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Trudeau%20declared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Trudeau%20also%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20shared%20our%20concerns%20with%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20and%20asked%20them%20to%20work%20with%20us...%26quot%3B.%20However%2C%20he%20claimed%20that%20these%20requests%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Brepeatedly%20refused%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20why...%20this%20weekend...%20Canadian%20officials%20took%20an%20extraordinary%20step.%20They%20met%20with%20Indian%20officials%20to%20share%20RCMP%20(Royal%20Canadian%20Mounted%20Police)%20evidence%2C%20which%20concluded%20six%20agents%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20are%20'persons%20of%20interest'%20in%20criminal%20activities.%20And%20despite%20repeated%20requests%20to%20the%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20they%20have%20decided%20not%20to%20co-operate...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Trudeau's%20allegations%20coincide%20with%20sliding%20support%20and%20tanking%20popularity%20ratings%2C%20and%20two%20electoral%20losses%20ahead%20of%20next%20year's%20elections.%20At%20Monday's%20press%20conference%20he%20said%20it%20was%20his%20%26quot%3Bresponsibility%20to%20take%20action%20and%20never%20hesitate%20to%20do%20what%20is%20necessary%20to%20protect%20Canadians%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20comments%20came%20after%20a%20RCMP%20Commissioner%20Mike%20Duheme%20and%20Assistant%20Commissioner%20Brigitte%20Gauvin%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Frcmp-india-expel-1.7351837%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewarned%20Canadians%20of%20a%20public%20safety%20threat%20but%20offered%20few%20details%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20would%20only%20say%20the%20RCMP%20has%20evidence%20pertaining%20to%20%26quot%3Bconnections%26quot%3B%20between%20a%20certain%20number%20of%20individuals%20arrested%20and%20charged%20for%20murder%20(eight%20people)%20and%20extortion%20(at%20least%2022)%20and%20the%20Government%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPressed%20on%20the%20current%20%26quot%3Bpublic%20safety%20threat%20to%20Canadians%26quot%3B%2C%20Mr%20Duheme%20called%20on%20Canadian%20citizens%20to%20come%20forward%20if%20faced%20with%20%26quot%3Bintimidation%2C%20harassment%2C%20coercion%2C%20or%20extortion%2C%20in%20any%20way%20or%20form%2C%20(to)%20obtain%20information%20for%20the%20Government%20of%20India%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20row%20spiked%20after%20Canada%20Foreign%20Minister%20Melanie%20Joly%2C%20acting%20on%20RCMP%20information%2C%20issued%20six%20Indian%20diplomats%20a%20deportation%20notice.%20%26quot%3BThey%20must%20leave%20Canada...%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Trudeau%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BLet%20me%20be%20clear...%20the%20evidence%20brought%20to%20light%20by%20the%20RCMP%20cannot%20be%20ignored...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-to-withdraw-high-commissioner-from-canada-in-massive-escalation-of-row-6788140%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndia%20To%20Withdraw%20High%20Commissioner%20Amid%20Escalation%20Of%20Canada%20Row%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20its%20side%2C%20Delhi%20has%20ramped%20up%20criticism%20of%20the%20Trudeau%20government%2C%20saying%20accusations%20against%20its%20envoy%2C%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20Verma%2C%20are%20%26quot%3Bludicrous%20and%20deserve%20to%20be%20treated%20with%20contempt%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpolitical-agenda-of-trudeau-government-indias-full-statement-slamming-canada-6785786%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BPolitical%20Agenda%20Of%20Trudeau%20Government%26quot%3B%3A%20India%20Slams%20Canada%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20also%20said%20that%20Mr%20Trudeau's%20%26quot%3Bhostility%20to%20India%20has%20long%20been%20in%20evidence%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSanjay%20Verma%20is%20India's%20senior-most%20serving%20diplomat%20with%20a%20distinguished%20career%20spanning%2036%20years.%20He%20has%20been%20an%20Ambassador%20in%20Japan%20and%20Sudan%2C%20while%20also%20serving%20in%20Italy%2C%20Turkiye%2C%20Vietnam%20and%20China%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20foreign%20ministry%20said%2C%20calling%20the%20allegations%20a%20%26quot%3Bstrategy%20of%20smearing%20India%20for%20political%20gains%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728965460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F644mqu68_trudeau-india-pc_625x300_15_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhardeep-singh-nijjar-killing-justin-trudeau-doubles-down-on-charges-after-india-canada-diplomatic-showdown-6791322%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Canada%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20late%20Monday%20doubled%20down%20on%20accusations%20of%20India%20%26quot%3Bsupporting%20criminal%20activity%20against%20Canadians%26quot%3B%2C%20as%20the%20two%20countries%20expel%20six%20diplomats%20each%20in%20the%20row%20over%20the%20killing%20of%20terrorist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20NIjjar.%22%2C%22autho