-ruling-alliance-nears-finishing-line-sources-6790068%5C%22%3ENDTV%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20party%20will%20contest%20on%20158%20of%20the%20state's%20288%20seats.%20It%20has%20offered%2070%20seats%20to%20Eknath%20Shinde's%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%2050%20to%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20battered%20by%20the%20Haryana%20defeat%2C%20will%20face%20an%20upbeat%20BJP.%20Among%20the%20key%20figures%20to%20be%20watched%20out%20in%20the%20poll%20season%20in%20Maharashtra%20will%20be%C2%A0Maratha%20quota%20activist%20Manoj%20Jarange%20Patil%2C%20who%20has%20held%20a%20series%20of%20hunger%20strikes%20to%20demand%20reservation%20for%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20held%20this%20year%2C%20MVA%20won%2030%20of%20the%20state's%2048%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%20The%20ruling%20alliance%20won%2017.%20One%20seat%20went%20to%20an%20Independent%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20in%20Jharkhand%2C%C2%A0Chief%20Minister%20Hemant%20Soren's%20Jharkhand%20Mukti%20Morcha%20(JMM)%20is%20ready%20to%20lock%20horns%20with%20the%20BJP.%20In%20the%202019%20elections%2C%20JMM%20had%20won%2030%20seats%20and%20went%20on%20to%20form%20the%20government%20with%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20has%20won%2016%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoubts%20over%20the%20future%20of%20this%20government%20when%20Mr%20Soren%20was%20arrested%20in%20a%20land%20scam%20case%20in%20January%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20party's%20Champai%20Soren%20to%20take%20over%20the%20chief%20ministerial%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoren%20said%20the%20JMM-led%20alliance%20will%20contest%20all%2081%20seats%20in%20the%20upcoming%20assembly%20elections.%20He%C2%A0expressed%20confidence%20in%20the%20party's%20electoral%20preparedness%20and%20asserted%20that%20the%20alliance%20would%20regain%20power%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20term%20of%20the%20Maharashtra%20assembly%20ends%20on%20November%2026%2C%20that%20of%20Jharkhand%20end