recent%20interaction%2C%20Gurjapneet%20recalled%20castling%20Kohli%20in%20the%20nets%2C%20which%20infuriated%20the%20star%20batter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20I%20bowled%20him%2C%20I%20looked%20at%20him%20and%20didn't%20dare%20to%20look%20at%20him%20again.%20He%20was%20very%2C%20very%20angry.%20But%20I%20realised%2C%20he%20was%20angry%20with%20himself%20more%20than%20anything.%20And%20after%20a%20straight%20drive%2C%20he%20again%20looked%20at%20me%20and%20smiled%2C%26quot%3B%20Gurjapneet%20told%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fgurjapneet-singh-virat-kohli-cheteshwar-pujara-tamil-nadu-vs-saurashtra-ranji-trophy-9618742%2F%5C%22%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Gurjapneet%20also%20revealed%20Kohli's%20advice%2C%20which%20helped%20him%20get%20the%20better%20of%20the%20Saurashtra%20batters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20told%20me%2C%20when%20there%20is%20no%20movement%2C%20change%20the%20angle%20and%20try%20bowling%20around%20the%20wicket.%20Because%20with%20that%20angle%2C%20even%20if%20you%20manage%20to%20get%20slight%20movement%2C%20it%20will%20end%20up%20troubling%20most%20batsmen%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20further%20revealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%C2%A0Kohli%20will%20be%20back%20in%20action%20on%20Wednesday%20as%20India%20take%20on%20New%20Zealand%20in%20the%20first%20Test%20in%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20young%20pacer%20also%20shed%20light%20on%20how%20he%20planned%20Pujara's%20dismissal%2C%20describing%20the%20latter%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Blegend%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20bowl%20to%20a%20legendary%20batsman%20like%20him%2C%20you%20have%20to%20be%20accurate%20from%20the%20word%20go.%20So%20the%20plan%20was%20to%20push%20him%20on%20the%20backfoot%20and%20then%20send%20in%20a%20good%20front%20foot%20ball%20that%20would%20make%20him%20uncomfortable.%20Having%20gone%20wicketless%20in%20the%20first%20innings%2C%20Bala%20bhai%2