0in%20Ohio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20plaintiff%20alleges%20that%20he%20was%20orally%20raped%20by%20Combs%20while%20working%20in%20the%20stockroom%20of%20the%20flagship%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20plaintiff%20said%20he%20worked%20for%20Ecko%2C%20a%20rival%20clothing%20company%20to%20Combs'%20Sean%20John%20brand%20that%20was%20also%20carried%20by%20Macy's.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20day%20of%20the%20attack%2C%20Combs%20entered%20into%20the%20stockroom%20with%20three%20armed%20bodyguards%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20or%20more%20of%20the%20guards%20struck%20him%20%E2%80%94%20he%20may%20have%20been%20pistol-whipped%2C%20he%20alleges%20%E2%80%94%20causing%20him%20to%20fall%20to%20his%20hands%20and%20knees%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20plaintiff%20says%20in%20the%20lawsuit%20that%20one%20or%20more%20of%20the%20bodyguards%20threatened%20to%20kill%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20plaintiff%20said%20Combs%20demanded%20he%20perform%20oral%20sex%20on%20him%2C%20calling%20him%20by%20the%20name%20of%20the%20company%20he%20worked%20for%2C%20%26quot%3BEcko.%26quot%3B%20Combs%20proceeded%20to%20orally%20rape%20the%20plaintiff%20in%20what%20was%20described%20as%20a%20two-minute%20attack%2C%20according%20to%20the%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20alleges%20that%20after%20the%20assault%2C%20Combs%20grabbed%20armfuls%20of%20Sean%20John%20merchandise%20from%20the%20stockroom%2C%20went%20out%20onto%20the%20retail%20floor%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bbegan%20passing%20out%20merchandise%20to%20an%20adoring%20crowd%2C%20as%20if%20nothing%20had%20happened.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20accuses%20Macy's%20of%20quickly%20covering%20up%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sean%20Combs%2C%20Cassie%20Ventura%2C%20and%20Terry%20Lundgren%20stand%20in%20front%20of%20a%20Macy's%20backdrop.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670d974c3f2165d716e0bcb7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5