the%20most%20recent.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20gradual%20transition%2C%20which%20is%20there%20inherently%20to%20show%20that%3A%20'Hey%2C%20as%20I%20was%20taking%20on%20more%20responsibilities%20and%20more%20work%2C%20I%20was%20doing%20more%20things%20which%20were%20more%20impactful%2C%20which%20I%20will%20do%20in%20a%20PM%20career%20as%20well.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECustomizing%20smaller%20sections%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Kulkarni%20selectively%20picked%20what%20would%20go%20into%20a%20section%20titled%20%26quot%3Btools.%26quot%3B%20He%20only%20picked%20skills%20that%20would%20overlap%20with%20a%20product%20management%20role%2C%20such%20as%20%26quot%3Bdefining%20strategy%2C%20working%20across%20stakeholders%2C%20and%20building%20relationships.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2219f6d549-83ba-455f-bcca-2e5ea1729fbc%5C%22%3ETwo%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20changes%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20would%20also%20change%20two%20main%20parts%20of%20his%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20today%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EData-focused%20approach%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20He%20would%20include%20details%20about%20how%20he%20used%20his%20data%20and%20statistical%20analysis%20skills.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20look%20at%20this%2C%20there's%20no%20mention%20of%20AI%20or%20anything%20in%20here.%20It%20doesn't%20talk%20about%20more%20data-oriented%20techniques%20like%20running%20AB%20experiments%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20For%20product%20managers%20%26quot%3Bin%20any%20industry%2C%20that's%20very%20important.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProjects%20outside%20work%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EKulkarni%20is%20an%20advisory%20board%20member%20at%20his%20alma%20mater%2C%20participates%20in%20AI%20societies%2C%20and%20writes%20scholarly%20articles%20about%20project%20management%20for%20an%20online%20publication.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20very%20key%20aspect%20of%20how%20I've%20grown%20in%20my%20career%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Learning%20about%20a%20new%20technology%20externally%20gives