f%20other%20earbuds%20in%20the%20%24150%20range%20can't%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20previous%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fapple-airpods-3rd-generation-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAirPods%203%3C%2Fa%3E%20earbuds%20weren't%20a%20slouch%20by%20any%20means%2C%20but%20the%20AirPods%204%20offer%20an%20improvement%20in%20overall%20audio%20performance%20thanks%20to%20their%20revised%20acoustic%20architecture%20and%20switch%20from%20the%20H1%20to%20H2%20chip.%20In%20practice%2C%20this%20upgrade%20leads%20to%20a%20touch%20more%20clarity%20and%20thump.%20However%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20recommend%20upgrading%20from%20the%203s%20to%204s%20strictly%20for%20sound%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20important%20to%20note%20that%20the%20base%20AirPods%204%20(%24129)%20and%20AirPods%204%20with%20ANC%20(%24179)%20have%20the%20same%20speaker%20system%20inside.%20I%20tested%20them%20both%2C%20and%20with%20ANC%20deactivated%2C%20I%20didn't%20hear%20a%20difference.%20So%20if%20you're%20purely%20concerned%20with%20audio%20playback%20and%20not%20blocking%20outside%20noise%2C%20you%20should%20be%20satisfied%20with%20the%20entry-level%20model.%20But%20for%20most%20users%2C%20I%20think%20the%20perks%20of%20ANC%20are%20worth%20the%20extra%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227cdee671-cc79-41c5-9036-fe9fb81f6916%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Noise%20cancellation%5C%22%3ENoise%20cancellation%20is%20solid%20despite%20the%20open%20design%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20pair%20of%20AirPods%204%20earbuds%20next%20to%20the%20case%20on%20an%20airplane%20tray%20table.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670d58e33f2165d716e0a5bf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Apple%20first%20announced%20that%20the%20AirPods%204%2