0for%20earbuds%20with%20ANC%2C%20or%20at%20least%20the%20most%20stereotypical%2C%20is%20on%20an%20airplane.%20There's%20a%20lot%20of%20engine%20noise%20that%20can%20drive%20people%20crazy.%20So%20I%20took%20the%20AirPods%204%20with%20ANC%20on%20a%20cross-country%20flight%20to%20see%20how%20they%20fared%20in%20that%20environment.%20The%20short%20answer%20is%20not%20very%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20earbuds%20did%20provide%20some%20noise%20relief%20%E2%80%94%20they%20can%20take%20the%20edge%20off%20%E2%80%94%20but%20not%20much%20compared%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-noise-cancelling-headphones%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20noise-canceling%20headphones%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20use%20an%20in-ear%20or%20over-ear%20design.%20The%20AirPods%20Pro%202%2C%20for%20example%2C%20do%20much%20better%20on%20an%20airplane.%20The%20best%20in-ear%20option%20is%20still%20the%20Bose%20QC%20Ultra%20Earbuds%2C%20which%20can%20nearly%20block%20this%20kind%20of%20noise%20entirely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20knock%20against%20the%20AirPods%204%20ANC%20performance%20is%20that%20I%20felt%20more%20of%20a%20pressure-like%20sensation%20in%20my%20ears%20than%20I%20have%20with%20other%20earbuds.%20To%20be%20clear%2C%20ANC%20doesn't%20actually%20create%20pressure%2C%20but%20the%20dulling%20of%20low%20frequencies%20can%20simulate%20this%20effect.%20It's%20not%20enough%20to%20make%20me%20stop%20turning%20on%20active%20noise%20canceling%2C%20but%20I've%20found%20this%20to%20be%20less%20of%20an%20issue%20on%20other%20headphones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20flip%20side%2C%20Apple's%20Transparency%20mode%20works%20incredibly%20well%20on%20the%20AirPods%204.%20This%20feature%20is%20like%20the%20opposite%20of%20ANC%2C%20and%20it%20uses%20the%20earbuds'%20microphones%20to%20let%20in%20outside%20noise%20so%20you%20can%20fully%20hear%20your%20surroundings.%20I%20quickly%20became%20hooked%20on%20this%20feature%20during%20my%20outdoor%20runs%20with%20the%20earbuds%20connected%20directly%20to%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-apple-watch%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%20Watch%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Transparency%20mode%20kept%20me%20fully%20aware%20of%20my%20surroundings%20while%20my%20music%20remained%20detailed%20and%20motivating.%20Occasionally%2C%20there%20were%20too%20many%20car%20horns%20or%20lots%20of%20construction%2C%20so%20I%20turned%20on%20Adaptive%20Audio%20to%20automatically%20minimize%20those%20bursts%20of%20noise.%20It's%20a%20subtle%20but%20important%20feature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2211ce7f42-b8f7-4156-9b4b-77faeb0e656e%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Charging%20case%5C%22%3EThe%20tiny%20case%20makes%20the%20AirPods%204%20easy%20to%20carry%20around%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20AirPods%204%20case%20in%20someone's%20hands.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670d59023f2165d716e0a5c5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20owned%20every%20pair%20of%20AirPods%20and%20their%20charging%20case%20has%20always%20been%20pocketable%2C%20but%20this%20new%20model%20shrinks%20the%20size%20even%20further.%20It's%20noticeable%20enough%20that%20I%20felt%20ever-so-slightly%20disoriented%20when%20holding%20the%20new%20case%20in%20my%20hand%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20It's%20so%20petite%20that%20it%20almost%20looks%20fake.%20The%20buds%20themselves%20can%20last%20for%20up%20to%20five%20hours%20without%20ANC%20or%20four%20with%20ANC%2C%20while%20the%20case%20offers%20up%20to%2030%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20most%20of%20Apple's%20latest%20devices%2C%20the%20case%20features%20a%20USB-C%20charging%20port%20instead%20of%20Lightning%2C%20so%20it%20can%20use%20the%20same%20connection%20as%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fiphone-16-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EiPhone%2016%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%2015%2C%20or%20modern%20iPad.%20You%20can%20also%20charge%20the%20AirPods%204%20directly%20from%20any%20of%20those%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20the%20AirPods%204%20with%20ANC%20case%20has%20a%20few%20extra%20features%20that%20the%20base%20AirPods%204%20case%20does%20not%20support.%20My%20favorite%20of%20the%20bunch%20is%20wireless%20charging.%20It's%20so%20easy%20to%20set%20the%20case%20down%20on%20any%20Qi-compatible%20charger%20to%20boost%20up%20the%20battery.%20Like%20the%20AirPods%20Pro%202%2C%20the%20case%20can%20also%20be%20powered%20up%20via%20an%20Apple%20Watch%20charger.%20It's%20super%20handy%20while%20traveling%2C%20but%20it's%20been%20helpful%20at%20my%20desk%20and%20at%20my%20bedside%20dock%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20had%20trouble%20keeping%20track%20of%20my%20AirPods%203%20in%20the%20past%20and%20often%20misplaced%20them%20in%20the%20tiny%20fifth%20jeans%20pocket%20for%20days%20at%20a%20time.%20The%20AirPods%204%20with%20ANC%20should%20be%20a%20little%20easier%20to%20locate%20because%20they%20now%20support%20Apple's%20Find%20My%20feature%20and%20have%20a%20built-in%20speaker%20that%20can%20emit%20noise%20if%20you%20lose%20them.%20Though%20not%20essential%2C%20these%20are%20convenient%20extras%20that%20help%20give%20the%20ANC%20model%20a%20bit%20more%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22edcb54bf-79f2-472e-bcf9-39a178821aeb%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20do%20they%20compare%20to%20AirPods%20Pro%202%3F%5C%22%3EThe%20AirPods%20Pro%202%20still%20have%20perks%2C%20but%20some%20may%20prefer%20the%20fit%20of%20the%20AirPods%204%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222843%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20pair%20of%20AirPods%204%20resting%20on%20a%20table.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670d59366ac7b701e7cae0d7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221895%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20semi-open%20fit%20is%20ideal%20for%20buyers%20who%20don't%20like%20the%20feel%20of%20in-ear%20buds%20that%20create%20a%20seal.%20%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20AirPods%204%20are%20positioned%20a%20step%20below%20Apple's%20AirPods%20Pro%202%2C%20and%20the%20Pro%20model%20still%20has%20some%20clear%20benefits.%20Most%20notably%2C%20the%20AirPods%20Pro%202%20have%20superior%20noise%20cancellation.%20They%20also%20feature%20a%20touch-sensitive%20control%20on%20the%20stems%20that%20lets%20you%20slide%20up%20or%20down%20to%20adjust%20volume.%20I%20wish%20this%20was%20carried%20over%20to%20the%20AirPods%204%20because%20it%20works%20so%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20upcoming%20software%20update%20will%20also%20add%20support%20for%20several%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-73657-20%26h%3D2ecbf2392a4b662eb8990560397d7e7310db756132bf7aa9d0926bee94c1ee00%26postID%3D670d2141e5b54083005594dd%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fapple-airpods-4-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.apple.com%252Fairpods-pro%252Fhearing-health%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaural%20health%20features%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0to%20the%20AirPods%20Pro%202%20that%20are%20missing%20on%20the%20AirPods%204.%20These%20features%20will%20include%20a%20hearing%20test%20and%20hearing%20aid%20functionality.%20There's%20also%20a%20hearing%20protection%20mode%20that%20can%20reduce%20volume%20in%20loud%20environments%20(like%20a%20concert)%20to%20prevent%20damage%20to%20your%20ears.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AirPods%20Pro%202%20also%20use%20a%20different%20ear-tip%20design%20than%20the%20AirPods%204%2C%20but%20whether%20this%20is%20a%20benefit%20or%20not%20is%20less%20clear-cut.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20fit%2C%20I%20actually%20prefer%20the%20AirPods%204.%20The%20AirPods%20Pro%202%20are%20slightly%20more%20bulbo