n%2C%20sources%20said%20after%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20held%20parallel%20strategy%20meets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20Maharashtra%20core%20group%20meet%20in%20Delhi%20was%20attended%20by%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20party%20chief%20J%20P%20Nadda.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20BJP%20president%20Chandrashekhar%20Bawankule%2C%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20and%20the%20party's%20national%20general%20secretary%20Vinod%20Tawde%20were%20among%20those%20present.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20blueprint%20settles%20the%20challenges%20the%20Mahayuti%20was%20facing%20-%20the%20high%20demands%20from%20alliance%20partners%20and%20the%20BJP's%20internal%20resistance%20to%20allotting%20seats%20to%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20faction%20of%20the%20NCP.%20The%20Shiv%20Sena%20was%20asking%20for%2090%20seats%20and%20the%20NCP%2070.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20alliance%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20is%20still%20at%20work%20trying%20to%20establish%20its%20broad%20roadmap.%20The%20parties%20are%20yet%20to%20sort%20out%20the%20tussle%20over%20some%20of%20the%20seats%2C%20including%20state%20capital%20Mumbai%20and%20Nagpur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20which%20also%20held%20a%20strategy%20meet%20earlier%20this%20evening%2C%20announced%20that%20the%20decision%20on%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20in%20Maharashtra%20will%20be%20taken%20after%20the%20elections%20-%20a%20situation%20that%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20faction%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20is%20deeply%20uncomfortable%20with.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Thackeray%20has%20repeatedly%20said%20an%20announcement%20about%20the%20Chief%20Ministerial%20candidate%2C%20whoever%20it%20is%2C%20should%20be%20made%20as%20early%20as%20possible.%20He%2C%20however%2C%20has%20maintained%20that%20the%20Opposition%20will%20wait%20till%20the%20ruling%20alliance%20shows%20its%20cards.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Congress%20meet%2C%20held%20in%20Delhi%20under%20the%20chairmanship%20of%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20the%20leaders%20were%20advised%20to%20avoid%20overconfidence%20like%20in%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20leaders%2C%20who%20included%20Maharashtra%20unit%20chief%20Nana%20Patole%20and%20Maharashtra%20in-charge%20Ramesh%20Chennithala%2C%20were%20advised%20to%20speak%20with%20caution%20on%20sensitive%20issues%20including%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20and%20Maratha%20reservation.%20Over-dependence%20on%20Jats%2C%20and%20short%20shrift%20to%20the%20OBCs%20had%20cost%20the%20Congress%20heavily%20in%20Haryana.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Maharashtra%20too%2C%20the%20BJP%20strategy%20includes%20consolidation%20of%20the%20OBC%20votes%20with%20various%20other%20communities%20to%20take%20on%20the%20MVA%20alliance%20of%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar%20and%20the%20Congress.%20The%20ruling%20alliance%20is%20also%20hopeful%20of%20winning%20a%20chunk%20of%20the%20Maratha%20vote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20November-December%20election%20in%20Maharashtra%20is%20one%20from%20which%20the%20Opposition%20has%20high%20hopes%2C%20having%20bested%20the%20ruling%20alliance%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20earlier%20this%20year.%20The%20results%2C%20they%20claimed%2C%20has%20decisively%20settled%20the%20question%20of%20which%20is%20the%20real%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20the%20real%20NCP%2C%20even%20though%20the%20Election%20Commission%20had%20awarded%20the%20party%20names%20and%20election%20symbols%20to%20the%20rebel%20factions%20in%20both%20cases.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20outcome%20was%20dismal%20for%20the%20ruling%20alliance%2C%20with%20the%20opposition%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20-the%20alliance%20of%20Congress%2C%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20faction%20of%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar%20faction%20of%20the%20NCP%20-%20winning%2030%20of%20the%20state's%2048%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%20The%20ruling%20alliance%20won%2017.%20One%20seat%20went%20to%20an%20Independent%20candidate.%