y.%20With%20a%20thick%2C%20double-walled%20construction%2C%20the%20hard-sided%20crate%20provides%20an%20incredible%20amount%20of%20protection%20for%20your%20dog%20%E2%80%94%20perfect%20for%20car%2C%20van%2C%20or%20pickup%20truck%20travel.%20If%20you're%20doubtful%2C%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiipgf_081717_best-dog-crates-20%26h%3D99d2c678fcdcadc217de7c2e465cb3c0a389de7ccaba0714d54fb6b3f15df845%26postID%3D61b8efc6f2a36b1ac9f4157c%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fbest-dog-crate%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fgunner.com%252Fpages%252Ftestimonials%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etestimonial%20page%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20crash%20victims%20and%20actual%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiipgf_081717_best-dog-crates-20%26h%3Da2e42c3ee75d966ad0ed0d5875c8b3721c3517416fd1a82a8b2af39b7f77be8a%26postID%3D61b8efc6f2a36b1ac9f4157c%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fbest-dog-crate%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fgunner.com%252Fblogs%252Fpack%253Fcategory%253DTest%252520Videos%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elab%20test%20videos%3C%2Fa%3E%20should%20put%20those%20fears%20to%20rest.%20In%20my%20testing%2C%20I%20couldn't%20find%20a%20single%20weak%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20kennel%20is%20also%20about%20as%20secure%20as%20they%20come%2C%20with%20a%20metal%20clasp%20lock%20that%20can%20be%20used%20as%20a%20key%20lock%20(two%20keys%20included)%20and%20built-in%20metal%20pins%20for%20tie-down%20straps.%20Thick%20rubber%20feet%20also%20keep%20the%20crate%20from%20sliding%20around.%20Although%20this%20extra%20protection%20translates%20to%20a%20heavier%20weight%20(the%20small%20size%20we%20tested%20weighed%2027%20pounds)%2C%20two%20heavy-duty%20carrying%20straps%20with%20rubber%20handles%20help%20make%20this%20less%20of%20an%20issue.%20Plus%2C%20chances%20are%20you'll%20be%20leaving%20it%20in%20your%20truck%20bed%20or%20van%20most%20of%20the%20time%20anyway.%20The%20smooth%20interior%20is%20easy%20to%20wipe%20clean%2C%20and%20it%20has%20a%20handy%20removable%20plug%2C%20allowing%20you%20to%20spray%20it%20down%20and%20drain%20without%20much%20hassle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222daebbb3-7beb-486d-9f40-d83aebda5a3d%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20to%20look%20for%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20dog%20crate%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20all%20dog%20crates%20are%20created%20equal%2C%20and%20certain%20models%20or%20types%20are%20better%20for%20different%20dogs%20and%20use%20cases.%20To%20help%20compile%20this%20list%20of%20key%20features%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%20when%20shopping%20for%20a%20dog%20crate%2C%20I%20interviewed%20a%20board-certified%20veterinary%20behaviorist%20and%20two%20professional%20dog%20trainers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESizing%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIt's%20essential%20that%20you%20choose%20a%20crate%20that%20is%20the%20proper%20size%20for%20your%20dog.%20%26quot%3BThe%20crate%20needs%20to%20be%20large%20enough%20for%20the%20dog%20to%20stand%20up%2C%20turn%20around%2C%20and%20lie%20down%20comfortably%20while%20spreading%20themselves%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Silletto%20says.%20All%20crate%20brands%20provide%20the%20internal%20dimensions%20of%20their%20crates%2C%20and%20some%20even%20do%20the%20work%20for%20you%20by%20telling%20you%20which%20size%20is%20best%20for%20your%20dog's%20specific%20measurements.%20If%20you%20have%20a%20puppy%2C%20look%20for%20a%20crate%20with%20a%20removable%20divider.%20This%20divider%20can%20be%20moved%20toward%20the%20back%20of%20the%20crate%20as%20your%20dog%20grows%2C%20increasing%20the%20size%20of%20its%20living%20space%20so%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20buy%20multiple%20crates%20for%20the%20same%20dog.%20Both%20of%20the%20wire%20crates%20in%20this%20guide%20include%20a%20removable%20divider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESecurity%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EYour%20crate%20should%20be%20secure%20enough%20to%20keep%20your%20dog%20from%20escaping%2C%20especially%20if%20it's%20intended%20for%20travel%20use.%20Look%20for%20door%20locks%20and%20latches%20that%20are%20strong%20and%20sturdy%20and%20aren't%20easily%20opened%20accidentally.%20For%20extra%20security%2C%20most%20plastic%20travel%20crates%20also%20have%20holes%20to%20slip%20zip-ties%20through%2C%20and%20heavy-duty%20options%2C%20like%20the%20Gunner%20G1%20Kennel%2C%20even%20have%20key%20locks.%20Keep%20in%20mind%20that%20soft%20crates%20lack%20the%20security%20of%20hard-sided%20options%3A%20%26quot%3BSoft%20crates%20can%20easily%20provide%20an%20escape%20route%20and%20are%20not%20safe%20for%20the%20dog%20to%20be%20left%20alone%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20Silletto%20says.%20Safety%20is%20also%20important%20when%20considering%20the%20security%20of%20your%20crate.%20%26quot%3BIt%20must%20not%20have%20any%20sharp%20edges%20or%20spaces%20where%20any%20body%20part%20can%20be%20caught%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vet.cornell.edu%2Fresearch%2Ffaculty%2Fkatherine-houpt-vmd-phd%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Katherine%20Houpt%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20veterinary%20behaviorist%20and%20professor%20at%20the%20Cornell%20University%20College%20of%20Veterinary%20Medicine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAppearance%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIf%20you're%20concerned%20about%20aesthetics%2C%20look%20for%20a%20crate%20that%20better%20matches%20your%20home%20decor.%20Wire%20crates%20and%20plastic%20travel%20crates%20all%20look%20pretty%20much%20the%20same%2C%20but%20soft-sided%20options%20are%20available%20in%20many%20colors.%20Wooden%20furniture%20crates%20tend%20to%20be%20the%20best-looking%20and%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20finish%2C%20can%20add%20a%20modern%2C%20stylish%20look%20to%20your%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPortability%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EConsider%20how%20portable%20you%20need%20your%20crate%20to%20be.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20plan%20on%20moving%20it%20from%20room%20to%20room%20or%20bringing%20it%20with%20you%20to%20travel%2C%20you%20want%20to%20think%20about%20collapsibility%20and%20weight%2C%26quot%3B%20Semel%20says.%20Plastic%20travel%20crates%20are%20designed%20primarily%20for%20transport%2C%20and%20although%20they're%20smaller%20than%20the%20average%20crate%2C%20their%20lighter%20weight%20and%20top-mounted%20handle%20make%20them%20well-suited%20for%20carrying.%20These%20are%20also%20the%20only%20crates%20intended%20to%20be%20moved%20with%20your%20dog%20inside.%20Although%20soft-sided%20crates%20cannot%20be%20moved%20with%20an%20animal%20inside%2C%20their%20light%20weight%20and%20folding%20design%20make%20them%20convenient%20to%20bring%20to%20a%20hotel%2C%20the%20beach%2C%20or%20another%20room%20in%20your%20house.%20While%20wire%20crates%20fold%20up%20and%20have%20carrying%20handles%2C%20they're%20still%20heavy%20and%20bulky%2C%20so%20not%20ideal%20for%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECleaning%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIf%20your%20dog%20is%20likely%20to%20make%20a%20mess%20with%20their%20food%20or%20water%20dish%2C%20or%20you%20have%20a%20puppy%20that's%20not%20house-trained%20yet%2C%20look%20for%20a%20crate%20that's%20easy%20to%20keep%20clean.%20Opt%20for%20plastic%20or%20wire%20over%20wood%20and%20fabric%2C%20and%20look%20for%20a%20crate%20with%20a%20removable%20floor%20tray.%20These%20plastic%20trays%20are%20convenient%20to%20remove%20without%20taking%20apart%20the%20crate%20and%20can%20be%20hosed%20or%20rinsed%20off%20easily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ba80176f-246c-43ed-a194-14daaee0fcbd%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20tested%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20tested%20the%20best%20dog%20crates%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20choose%20the%20best%20dog%20crates%2C%20I%20ran%20each%20model%20through%20a%20comprehensive%20testing%20process.%20Through%20extensive%20online%20research%20and%20input%20from%20our%20experts%2C%20I%20used%20these%20nine%20factors%20to%20evaluate%20and%20compare%20each%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStructural%20strength%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETo%20compare%20the%20overall%20strength%20and%20durability%20of%20the%20structure%20itself%2C%20I%20used%20a%20luggage%20scale%20with%20a%20looped%20hook%20to%20apply%20a%20consistent%20amount%20of%20pulling%20force%20to%20the%20doors%2C%20sides%2C%20and%20top%20of%20each%20crate.%20I%20noted%20excessive%20bending%20or%20signs%20of%20weakness%20in%20the%20material%20and%20assembly%20connections%2C%20paying%20close%20attention%20to%20the%20stability%20of%20the%20door%20and%20lock%20mechanism.%20The%20digital%20readout%20of%20the%20luggage%20scale%20allowed%20me%20to%20apply%20a%20consistent%2030%20pounds%20of%20pulling%20force%20for%20every%20test%2C%20although%20some%20crates%20had%20more%20points%20to%20attach%20to%20the%20scale%20than%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESecurity%20and%20safety%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20operated%20each%20door%20lock%2C%20latch%20system%2C%20and%20zipper%2030%20times%2C%20looking%20for%20signs%20of%20wear%20or%20vulnerability.%20We%20also%20paid%20close%20attention%20to%20any%20indications%20that%20the%20door%20could%20open%20accidentally.%20To%20better%20determine%20the%20safety%20of%20the%20crates%2C%20we%20looked%20for%20any%20sharp%20corners%20or%20other%20design%20flaws%20that%20could%20injure%20a%20dog.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPortability%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETo%20judge%20how%20convenient%20the%20crate%20is%20to%20move%20from%20room%20to%20room%2C%20we%20carried%20each%20one%2C%20except%20for%20the%20heavy%20wooden%20models%20that%20are%20not%20designed%20to%20be%20carried%2C%20through%20our%20house%20and%20into%20our%20car.%20For%20crates%20recommended%20for%20transport%20with%20a%20dog%20inside%2C%20we%20used%20a%2020-pound%20sandbag%20to%20simulate%20a%20pet%2C%20paying%20close%20attention%20to%20the%20structural%20stability%20of%20the%20crate%20and%20the%20carrying%20handle%20on%20top.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUsability%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETo%20evaluate%20overall%20usability%2C%20I%20set%20up%20and%20broke%20down%20each%20crate%20designed%20to%20do%20so%20three%20times%2C%20noting%20whether%20it%20was%20straightforward%20or%20complicated.%20I%20also%20evaluated%20the%20instruction%20manuals%20to%20gauge%20how%20clear%20and%20helpful%20they%20were.%20Finally%2C%20I%20considered%20how%20easy%20and%20comfortable%20it%20was%20to%20use%20components%20like%20door%20latches%20or%20carrying%20handles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECleaning%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETo%20simulate%20a%20soiled%20crate%2C%20I%20smeared%20dog%20food%20on%20the%20bottom%20and%20interior%20of%20the%20walls%2C%20waited%20an%20hour%2C%20and%20then%20cleaned%20it%20off%20the%20best%20I%20could.%20I%20noted%20if%20the%20surfaces%20were%20smooth%20and%20easy%20to%20wipe%20up%2C%20or%20porous%20and%20with%20lingering%20odor%20after%20cleaning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStorage%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20compared%20the%20overall%20size%20of%20each%20crate%20and%20the%20folded-down%20dimensions%2C%20when%20applicable%2C%20to%20determine%20how%20convenient%20it%20would%20be%20to%20store%20each%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAppearance%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAlthough%20this%20factor%20is%20a%20bit%20subjective%2C%20I%20considered%20each%20crate's%20overall%20look%20and%20style.%20I%20also%20noted%20the%20number%20of%20color%20options%20offered%20by%20each%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFunctionality%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20evaluated%20each%20crate's%20additional%20features%2C%20such%20as%20multiple%20doors%20for%20easy%20access%2C%20removable%20handles%2C%20bedding%2C%20or%20adjustable%20space%20dividers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESize%20options%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETo%20ensure%20people%20can%20get%20the%20correct%20size%20crate%20for%20their%20dog%2C%20I%20noted%20the%20range%20of%20sizes%20offered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDog%20crates%20FAQs%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ten%20different%20dog%20crates%20are%20arranged%20and%20stacked%20in%20a%20room.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670d68086ac7b701e7cae725%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThere%20are%20many%20different%20types%20of%20dog%20crates%2C%20including%20wire%20frame%2C%20soft-sided%2C%20plastic%2C%20and%20wooden%20crates.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Rennie%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%3EDo%20vets%20recommend%20dog%20crates%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20veterinarians%2C%20trainers%2C%20and%20breeders%20recommend%20crate%20training%20dogs%20from%20a%20young%20age%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.akc.org%2Fexpert-advice%2Ftraining%2Fwhy-crate-training-is-great-for-your-dog%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DMost%2520veterinarians%252C%2520trainers%252C%2520and%2520breeders%2Chave%2520to%2520clean%2520up%2520messes.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20Kennel%20Club%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Veterinary%20behaviorist%20Houpt%20says%20a%20crate%20is%20useful%20for%20house%20training%20and%20travel.%20%26quot%3BIn%20addition%2C%20some%20dogs%20seem%20to%20feel%20secure%20in%20their%20crates%20so%20will%20relax%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20That%20being%20said%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20know%20that%20veterinarians%20and%20dog%20trainers%20make%20it%20very%20clear%20that%20dogs%20should%20not%20be%20kept%20in%20crates%20for%20long%20periods.%20Silletto%20says%20you%20should%20not%20crate%20your%20dog%20for%20more%20than%20four%20hours%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20inhumane%20to%20crate%20a%20dog%20for%2040%20hours%20a%20week%20and%20will%20erode%20the%20positive%20association%20with%20their%20crate.%26quot%3B%20And%2C%20if%20you%20are%20unable%20to%20monitor%20your%20dog%20while%20they're%20in%20the%20crate%2C%20you%20should%20remove%20any%20collar%20or%20harness%2C%20which%20could%20become%20trapped%20in%20parts%20of%20the%20crate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20kind%20of%20crate%20is%20best%20for%20dogs%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20crate%20for%20dogs%20depends%20on%20that%20animal's%20specific%20wants%20and%20your%20needs.%20A%20basic%20wire%20crate%20should%20suffice%20if%20you're%20using%20it%20primarily%20in%20your%20home%20and%20won't%20be%20moving%20it%20much.%20However%2C%20some%20dogs%20prefer%20a%20more%20den-like%20environment%2C%20so%20covering%20it%20with%20a%20blanket%20may%20be%20helpful.%20If%20your%20dog%20is%20prone%20to%20pulling%20the%20blanket%20inside%20for%20chewing%2C%20you%20might%20want%20to%20consider%20a%20different%20type%20of%20crate.%20For%20dogs%20traveling%20to%20a%20vet%20appointment%20or%20on%20an%20airplane%2C%20a%20plastic%20kennel-style%20crate%20will%20keep%20them%20comfortable%20and%20safe%20while%20being%20carried%20around.%20The%20best%20crate%20for%20dedicated%20car%20or%20truck%20bed%20travel%20is%20one%20that%20is%20crash-tested%2C%20like%20the%20Gunner%20G1%20Kennel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20is%20the%20purpose%20of%20a%20dog%20crate%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20purpose%20of%20a%20dog%20crate%20depends%20on%20your%20specific%20needs%2C%20but%20in%20a%20nutshell%2C%20it's%20to%20provide%20a%20comfortable%20and%20relaxing%20space%20for%20your%20dog%20to%20be%20confined.%20By%20preventing%20your%20dog%20from%20wandering%20on%20their%20own%2C%20you%20can%20also%20productively%20teach%20house%20training%20and%20chew%20training%20without%20having%20to%20monitor%20your%20dog's%20behavior%20and%20location%20constantly.%20%26quot%3BDogs%20instinctively%20keep%20their%20rest%20area%20clean%20and%20will%20not%20relieve%20themselves%20on%20their%20bedding%2C%26quot%3B%20Silletto%20says.%20%26quot%3BThis%20allows%20you%20to%20better%20control%20when%20they%20go%20to%20the%20bathroom%20(outside)%20and%20makes%20it%20easier%20to%20reward%20them%20for%20it.%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20is%20the%20best%20brand%20for%20dog%20crates%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20brand%20for%20you%20will%20depend%20on%20your%20needs.%20Frisco%20and%20Midwest%20are%20popular%2C%20well-regarded%20brands%20for%20most%20crates%2C%20while%20Gunner%20is%20a%20phenomenally%20good%20brand%20for%20vehicular%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20type%20of%20crates%20do%20dogs%20prefer%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EDogs%20prefer%20the%20type%20of%20crate%20that%20makes%20them%20feel%20comfortable%20and%20relaxed%20inside.%20Regardless%20of%20whether%20a%20crate%20is%20wire%2C%20plastic%2C%20or%20wood%2C%20it's%20much%20more%20important%20to%20create%20a%20positive%20association%20between%20the%20dog%20and%20the%20crate.%20To%20do%20so%2C%20Houpt%20recommends%20placing%20a%20dog's%20favorite%20toys%20in%20it%20for%20several%20days%20and%20rolling%20balls%20into%20it%20for%20several%20days%20until%20the%20dog%20willingly%20enters.%20At%20that%20point%2C%20close%20the%20door%20only%20part%20way%20and%20wait%20a%20few%20days%20before%20closing%20it%20completely.%20Another%20way%20to%20form%20a%20positive%20relationship%20between%20your%20dog%20and%20the%20crate%2C%20according%20to%20Silletto%2C%20is%20to%20hide%20treats%20in%20the%20crate.%20%26quot%3BThis%20way%2C%20the%20dog%20is%20rewarded%20when%20they%20spontaneously%20go%20inside%20the%20crate%20on%20their%20own%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20is%20the%20best%20crate%20for%20a%20dog%20to%20sleep%20in%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20dog%20crate%20to%20sleep%20in%20is%20one%20that's%20small%20enough%20to%20provide%20a%20den-like%20environment.%20Depending%20on%20the%20dog%2C%20a%20more%20enclosed%20option%2C%20like%20the%20Frisco%20Double%20Door%20Furniture%20Style%20Dog%20Crate%2C%20could%20provide%20an%20even%20cozier%20environment%20for%20overnight%20use.%20Semel%20says%20that%20the%20flooring%20or%20bedding%20also%20affects%20a%20dog's%20comfort.%20%26quot%3BSome%20dogs%20get%20too%20warm%2C%20so%20a%20plush%20or%20fuzzy%20mat%20may%20be%20too%20much%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20you%20may%20need%20to%20try%20out%20different%20options%20and%20that%20some%20dogs%20may%20prefer%20just%20a%20blanket%20or%20large%20stuffed%20toy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3ECan%20I%20use%20a%20dog%20crate%20for%20travel%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ESemel%20recommends%20crates%20for%20travel%2C%20adding%20that%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bportable%20bedroom%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20crate%20allows%20your%20dog%20to%20have%20the%20same%20routine%20while%20away%20from%20home.%20Keep%20in%20mind%2C%20however%2C%20that%20a%20dog's%20collar%20or%20harness%20could%20become%20caught%20between%20the%20wires%20of%20a%20crate%2C%20so%20you%20should%20remove%20any%20collars%20or%20harnesses%20for%20their%20safety.%20Plastic%2C%20kennel-style%20options%20are%20lighter%20weight%20than%20other%20models%20and%20have%20handles%20on%20top%20so%20you%20can%20easily%20carry%20them%20with%20your%20dog%20inside.%20If%20you%20frequently%20drive%20with%20your%20dog%20or%20transport%20them%20in%20the%20back%20of%20a%20pickup%20truck%2C%20the%20crash-tested%20Gunner%20G1%20Kennel%20is%20a%20perfect%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-dog-crate%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728932370000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670d5bb46ac7b701e7cae1cc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-dog-crate%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22We%20tested%20and%20rated%20the%20best%20dog%20crates%20for%20small%20and%20big%20dogs.%20Our%20top%20picks%20include%20extra%20large%20wire%20models%20with%20dividers%20and%20furniture%20crates.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Alex%20Rennie%2CSorin%20McKnight)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-dog-crate%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'You%20know%20what%20you%20are%20here%20for'%3A%20College%20