connections%20to%20a%20nearby%20scrap%20shop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conspiracy%20took%20shape%20over%20several%20meetings%2C%20with%20promises%20of%20substantial%20payment%20upon%20successful%20%26quot%3Bexecution%20of%20the%20plan%26quot%3B.%20The%20shooters%20were%20given%20an%20advance%20of%20Rs%2050%2C000%20each.%20They%20purchased%20a%20motorcycle%20to%20monitor%20Mr%20Siddique's%20routine%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPravin%20Lonkar%20is%20accused%20of%20drafting%20two%20shooters%20to%20target%20Siddique%20and%20identified%20by%20police%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bco-conspirator%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cops%20are%20on%20the%20hunt%20to%20catch%20the%20suspected%20%26quot%3Bhandler%26quot%3B%2C%20Mohammad%20Yasin%20Akhtar%2C%20and%20shooter%20Gautam%2C%20who%20allegedly%20fired%20at%20the%20senior%20politician.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20on%20Sunday%20said%20the%20third%20accused%20in%20the%20Baba%20Siddique%20murder%20case%20will%20be%20arrested%20%26quot%3Bsoon%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20investigation%20disclosed%20that%20it%20was%20Gautam%20who%20called%20Kashyap%20to%20work%20with%20him%20in%20Pune%20three%20months%20ago%2C%20the%20police%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubsequently%2C%20Gautam%20relocated%20to%20Vinoba%20Bhave%20Nagar%20locality%20in%20Kurla%20in%20Mumbai%20in%20September%20last%20year%20and%20started%20staying%20on%20rent.%20He%20roped%20in%20Singh%20in%20the%20conspiracy%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20three%20shooters-%20Singh%2C%20Kashyap%2C%20and%20Gautam-%20were%20paid%20Rs%2050%2C000%20each%20upfront.%20Investigations%20have%20revealed%20that%20the%20three%20accused%20used%20to%20travel%20from%20Kurla%20(where%20they%20lived%20on%20rent)%20to%20Bandra%20every%20day%2C%20mostly%20in%20auto%20rickshaws%2C%20and%20recce%20the%20places%20Baba%20Siddiqui%20and%20his%20son%20used%20to%20frequent.%20These%20places%20included%20areas%20around%20th