%20his%20custody%20in%20a%20case%20registered%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20With%20inputs%20from%20PTI%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728925380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fbnhqfda_baba-siddique-murder_625x300_14_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbaba-siddique-shooters-were-given-flex-banner-to-identify-target-cops-6789477%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20plot%20to%20kill%20former%20Maharashtra%20minister%20Baba%20Siddique%20was%20hatched%20over%20100%20km%20away%20in%20Pune%20months%20ago%20during%20several%20meetings.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbaba-siddique-shooters-were-given-flex-banner-to-identify-target-cops-6789477%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22T20%20WC%3A%20India%20Out%20Of%20Semis%20Race%20As%20New%20Zealand%20Thrash%20Pakistan%20To%20Advance%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPakistan%20Women%C2%A0vs%20New%20Zealand%20Women%C2%A0Highlights%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20India's%20hopes%20of%20entering%20the%20Women's%20T20%20World%20Cup%20were%20dashed%20on%20Monday%20following%20Pakistan's%20heavy%20loss%20to%20New%20Zealand%20in%20Dubai.%20Despite%20some%20sloppy%20fielding%2C%20Pakistan%20managed%20to%20restrict%20New%20Zealand%20to%20110%2F6.%20Chasing%20a%20target%20of%20111%2C%20Pakistan%20were%20bowled%20out%20for%20a%20paltry%20total%20of%2056%20as%20captain%20Fatima%20Sana%20top-scored%20with%20a%20knock%20of%2021.%20With%20the%20win%2C%20New%20Zealand%20joined%20Australia%20in%20the%20semi-finals%20from%20Group%20A.%20The%20White%20Ferns%20ended%20the%20group%20stage%20with%20six%20points%2C%20two%20more%20than%20India.%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fpak-w-vs-nz-w-scorecard-live-cricket-score-icc-women-s-t20-world-cup-2024-match-19-pkwnzw10142024244951%5C%22%3EScorecard%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fp%3E%