3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20was%20a%20dreamer%20and%20a%20visionary.%20India%20was%20his%20national%20pride.%20He%20loved%20his%20country%2C%20the%20people.%20He'd%20say%20it%20was%20so%20important%20to%20globalise.%20'The%20only%20reason%20why%20I%20need%20to%20go%20global%20is%20to%20bring%20technology%20to%20India%20and%20upgrade%20our%20own%20companies%20to%20make%20better%20platforms'%2C%20Ratan%20Tata%20would%20say%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Radia%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20explained%20why%20Ratan%20Tata%20decided%20on%20making%20the%20'Rs%201%20lakh%20car'%20Nano%2C%20a%20statement%20which%20has%20been%20narrated%20many%20times%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20wanted%20something%20for%20the%20common%20person.%20He%20wanted%20a%20person%20on%20a%20bike%20to%20not%20get%20wet%20in%20the%20rain%2C%20for%20example.%20A%20newspaper%20had%20said%20Ratan%20Tata%20wanted%20a%20Rs%201%20lakh%20car.%20But%20we%20had%20never%20given%20a%20number%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20former%20chairperson%20of%20the%20defunct%20company%20Vaishnavi%20Corporate%20Communications%2C%20who%20had%20an%20inside%20view%20of%20some%20of%20the%20most%20crucial%20decisions%20made%20by%20the%20Tata%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtvprofit.com%2Fbusiness%2Fniira-radia-shares-ratan-tata-anecdotes-legacy-humility-and-vision%3Fsrc%3Dtl_story%5C%22%3ENiira%20Radia%20Recounts%20Her%20Association%20With%20Humble%20Leader%20Ratan%20Tata%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20why%20Ratan%20Tata%20chose%20Singur%20in%20West%20Bengal%20as%20the%20site%20for%20building%20the%20Nano%2C%20Ms%20Radia%20said%20the%20industrialist%20simply%20had%20his%20heart%20set%20on%20Bengal%20to%20create%20jobs%20and%20bring%20industrialization.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20announced%20Singur.%20It%20really%20surprised%20me%20because%20we%20were%20not%20told%20about%20the%20location%20earlier.%20It%20was%20natural%20for%20him.%20Why%20shouldn't%20it%20be%20Singur%3F%20He%20was%20for%20development%2C%20not%20to%20play%20politics%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Radia%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETata%20group%20was%20in%20talks%20on%20the%20big-ticket%20Corus%20deal%20when%20the%20huge%20battle%20over%20the%20Nano%20plant%20in%20Bengal%20erupted%2C%20Ms%20Radia%20told%20NDTV%2C%20adding%20they%20were%20in%20Bengal%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20two%20critical%20decisions%20-%20a%20bid%20was%20going%20on%20for%20Corus%2C%20and%20there%20was%20trouble%20on%20the%20ground%20in%20Singur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20should%20the%20Rs%201-lakh%20car%20be%20not%20built%20in%20Bengal%3F%20His%20dream%20was%20to%20industrialise%20the%20state...%20I%20think%20this%20Rs%201%20lakh%20number%20was%20there%20because%20he%20must%20have%20done%20his%20calculation%20at%20that%20time%2C%20that%20it%20may%20be%20possible.%20Of%20course%20he%20was%20criticised%20too.%20But%20the%20man%20had%20a%20dream%2C%20he%20had%20a%20vision.%20Those%20were%20more%20important%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Radia%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20was%20disappointed%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added%2C%20on%20the%20Nano%20not%20reaching%20heights%20Ratan%20Tata%20may%20have%20envisaged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20price%20point%20changed%20subsequently.%20I%20want%20to%20stay%20focused%20on%20who%20he%20was%2C%20not%20the%20business%20side.%20When%20he%20went%20to%20Bengal%2C%20he%20felt%20it%20needed%20to%20be%20industrialised.%20He%20wanted%20to%20create%20jobs.%20The%20whole%20road%20from%20Kolkata%20to%20Singur%20could%20have%20been%20developed%20beautifully.%20It%20(Nano%20project)%20went%20to%20Sanand%20(in%20Gujarat).%20Today%2C%20Sanand%20is%20like%20Gurugram%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Radia%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fniira-radia-recounts-when-ratan-tatas-dog-went-missing-on-marine-drive-6788598%5C%22%3ENiira%20Radia%20Recounts%20When%20Ratan%20Tata's%20Dog%20Went%20Missing%20On%20Marine%20Drive%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Singur%20problem%20was%20not%20about%20the%20Nano%20or%20Ratan%20Tata%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fight%20was%20a%20political%20fight.%20Singur%20was%20the%20constituency%20of%20a%20leader%20of%20the%20then%20ruling%20party...%20We%20visited%20many%20other%20states%20to%20look%20for%20a%20site.%20We%20were%20also%20called%20by%20Punjab%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20many%20others...%20We%20went%20to%20Gujarat%20as%20it%20was%20a%20bit%20more%20industrialised%20and%20moving%20towards%20development%2C%20so%20it%20would%20be%20easy%20to%20set%20up%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ms%20Radia%2C%20who%20handled%20public%20relations%20for%20the%20Tata%20group%20between%202000%20and%202012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Radia%20headed%20Vaishnavi%20Communications%20during%20the%20most%20critical%20time%20when%20the%20Tata%20group%20decided%20to%20consolidate%20its%20brand%20at%20the%20group%20level.%20She%20also%20remained%20a%20dear%20friend%20and%20a%20close%20confidante%20of%20Ratan%20Tata%20till%20his%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728919440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F3h5c2718_niira-radia_625x300_14_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-a-first-niira-radia-shares-why-ratan-tata-decided-to-build-the-tata-nano-6788793%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20corporate%20public%20relations%20professional%20Niira%20Radia%20in%20her%20first%20media%20interview%20in%20over%2012%20years%20and%20the%20first%20ever%20on%20the%20Tata%20group%20shared%20snippets%20from%20the%20time%20she%20worked%20with%20industrialist%20and%20philanthropist%20Ratan%20Tata%2C%20who%20died%20at%2086.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-a-first-niira-radia-shares-wh