1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20To%20Withdraw%20High%20Commissioner%20From%20Canada%20In%20Massive%20Escalation%20Of%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20decided%20to%20withdraw%20its%20High%20Commissioner%20in%20Canada%20after%20Ottawa%20linked%20him%20and%20some%20other%20Indian%20diplomats%20to%20the%20killing%20of%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20no%20faith%20in%20the%20current%20Canadian%20Government's%20commitment%20to%20ensure%20their%20security%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20government%20conveyed%20to%20the%20Canadian%20Charge%20d'Affaires%20who%20was%20summoned%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20this%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20underlined%20that%20in%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20extremism%20and%20violence%2C%20the%20Trudeau%20Government's%20actions%20endangered%20their%20safety.%20We%20have%20no%20faith%20in%20the%20current%20Canadian%20Government's%20commitment%20to%20ensure%20their%20security.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20has%20decided%20to%20withdraw%20the%20High%20Commissioner%20and%20other%20targeted%20diplomats%20and%20officials%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20foreign%20ministry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ties%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20plunged%20further%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-summons-canada-envoy-as-diplomatic-row-escalates-massively-6787530%5C%22%3ECanada%20said%20it%20was%20investigating%20the%20Indian%20High%20Commissioner%20%3C%2Fa%3Eas%20a%20%26quot%3Bperson%20of%20interest%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20Nijjar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Foreign%20Ministry%20received%20a%20%26quot%3Bdiplomatic%20communication%20from%20Canada%20yesterday%20suggesting%20that%20the%20Indian%20High%20Commissioner%20and%20other%20diplomats%20are%20'persons%20of%20interest'%20in%20a%20matter%20related%20to%20an%20investigation%20in%20that%20country%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20that%20the%20aspersions%20cast%20on%20High%20Commissioner%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20Verma%20by%20Canada%20were%20%26quot%3Bludicrous%26quot%3B.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHigh%20Commissioner%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20Verma%20is%20India's%20senior-most%20serving%20diplomat%20with%20a%20distinguished%20career%20spanning%2036%20years.%20He%20has%20been%20an%20Ambassador%20in%20Japan%20and%20Sudan%2C%20while%20also%20serving%20in%20Italy%2C%20Turkiye%2C%20Vietnam%20and%20China.%20The%20aspersions%20cast%20on%20him%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20Canada%20are%20ludicrous%20and%20deserve%20to%20be%20treated%20with%20contempt%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20foreign%20ministry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20%26quot%3Bpreposterous%26quot%3B%20allegations%2C%20terming%20them%20a%20%26quot%3Bstrategy%20of%20smearing%20India%20for%20political%20gains%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20also%20informed%20the%20senior%20diplomat%20of%20Canada%20this%20evening%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bbaseless%20targeting%20of%20the%20Indian%20High%20Commissioner%20and%20other%20diplomats%20and%20officials%20in%20Canada%20was%20completely%20unacceptable%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20conveyed%20that%20India%20reserves%20the%20right%20to%20take%20further%20steps%20in%20response%20to%20the%20Trudeau%20Government's%20support%20for%20extremism%2C%20violence%20and%20separatism%20against%20India%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20statement%20this%20morning%20slammed%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Trudeau's%20%26quot%3Bhostility%20to%20India%26quot%3B%2C%20adding%2C%20in%202018%2C%20his%20visit%20to%20India%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhich%20was%20aimed%20at%20currying%20favour%20with%20a%20vote%20bank%2C%20rebounded%20to%20his%20discomfort%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20Cabinet%20has%20included%20individuals%20who%20have%20openly%20associated%20with%20an%20extremist%20and%20separatist%20agenda%20regarding%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20India%20curbed%20visas%20for%20Canadians%20and%20forced%20Ottawa%20to%20withdraw%20diplomats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20dip%20in%20the%20ties%20comes%20just%20days%20after%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20meeting%20with%20Justin%20Trudeau%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20ASEAN%20Summit%20in%20Laos.%20While%20Trudeau%20described%20the%20meeting%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bbrief%20exchange%26quot%3B%2C%20sources%20in%20New%20Delhi%20said%20there%20was%20no%20substantive%20discussion%20between%20the%20two%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20and%20Trudeau's%20first%20meeting%20after%20Canada%20raised%20allegations%20regarding%20Nijjar's%20death%20was%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20G7%20Summit%20in%20Italy%20in%20June%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20been%20maintaining%20that%20the%20main%20issue%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20is%20that%20of%20Canada%20-%20home%20to%20around%207%2C70%2C000%20Sikhs%20-%20giving%20space%20to%20pro-Khalistan%20elements%20%26quot%3Boperating%20from%20their%20soil%20with%20impunity%26quot%3B%2C%20sources%20in%20New%20Delhi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrudeau%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20insisted%20that%20his%20stand%20on%20the%20matter%20remains%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728916920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2018-03%2Fpm-modi-justin-trudeau-pti_650x400_61519877647.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-to-withdraw-high-commissioner-from-canada-in-massive-escalation-of-row-6788140%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government%20has%20decided%20to%20withdraw%20its%20High%20Commissioner%20in%20Canada%20after%20Ottawa%20linked%20him%20and%20some%20other%20Indian%20diplomats%20to%20the%20killing%20of%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonic