%20at%20a%20government%20hospital%20is%20no%20answer%20to%20what%20the%20statute%20says.%20Sick%20or%20infirm%20means%20you%20can%20be%20granted%20bail%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20while%20presiding%20over%20a%20three-judge%20bench%20hearing%20the%20interim%20bail%20petition%20of%2067-year-old%20Amar%20Sadhuram%20Mulchandani%2C%20former%20chairperson%20of%20Seva%20Vikas%20Co-operative%20Bank%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20in%20July%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20or%20PMLA%20is%20non-bailable%20since%20unlike%20other%20laws%2C%20the%20accused%20here%20has%20to%20prove%20that%20he%20is%20not%20guilty.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnAn%20accused%20gets%20bail%20only%20when%20the%20court%20is%20satisfied%20that%20there%20are%20reasonable%20grounds%20for%20believing%20that%20he%20is%20not%20guilty%20of%20the%20offense%2C%20and%20not%20likely%20to%20commit%20any%20offense%20while%20on%20bail.%20Even%20so%2C%20the%20public%20prosecutor%20has%20to%20be%20given%20an%20opportunity%20to%20oppose%20bail.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20provision%20---%20listed%20under%20Section%2045%20of%20the%20law%20-%20was%20upheld%20earlier%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20today%20said%20the%20%26quot%3BProviso%20to%20Section%2045%20(1)%20of%20PMLA%20specifically%20contemplates%20that%20a%20person%20who%20'is%20sick%20or%20infirm'%20may%20be%20released%20on%20bail%20if%20the%20special%20court%20so%20directs%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20several%20people%2C%20including%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party's%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20Manish%20Sisodia%20and%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi's%20K%20Kavita%20had%20got%20bail%2C%20though%20after%20spending%20months%20in%20jail.%20AAP's%20Satyendar%20Jain%20had%20also%20got%20interim%20bail%20last%20year%20on%20health%20grounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728912240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F6f5n98uo_supreme-court_625x300_03_October_24.jpg%22%