nd%20Binod%20(on%20the%20Right)%20applying%20ointment%20on%20a%20sick%20dog%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-10-1728641747.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-10-1728641747-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-10-1728641747-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-10-1728641747-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-10-1728641747-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-369897%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENurzin%20Angmo%20(on%20the%20Left)%20and%20Binod%20(on%20the%20Right)%20applying%20ointment%20on%20a%20sick%20dog%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20keep%20the%20dogs%20we%20feel%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20survive%20outside%20on%20their%20own%20and%20release%20those%20who%20can%2C%20to%20where%20we%20originally%20found%20them.%20Dogs%20from%20one%20pen%20can%20be%20released%20to%20play%20in%20the%20central%20area%20and%20then%20returned%20to%20their%20pen.%20Inside%20the%20pens%2C%20the%20dogs%20are%20mostly%20free%20to%20exercise%20and%20play%20also%2C%20and%20there%20are%20cages%20provided%20for%20those%20who%20need%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Deena.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-1-Deena-Binod-1728640192.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Deena%20Talbot%20and%20Binod%20Aryal%20with%20the%20dogs%20at%20the%20shelter.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2