e%20people%20explaining%20to%20them%20what%20is%20happening%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalled%20in%20the%20TEDx%20Talk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSnapinsta.app_69213333_365858707698737_584681726921602045_n_1080-1728657159.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20general%20public%20gathered%20at%20a%20'Street%20Reopening'%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSnapinsta.app_69213333_365858707698737_584681726921602045_n_1080-1728657159.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSnapinsta.app_69213333_365858707698737_584681726921602045_n_1080-1728657159-300x218.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSnapinsta.app_69213333_365858707698737_584681726921602045_n_1080-1728657159-500x363.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSnapinsta.app_69213333_365858707698737_584681726921602045_n_1080-1728657159-768x558.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSnapinsta.app_69213333_365858707698737_584681726921602045_n_1080-1728657159-150x109.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-370033%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22784%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20general%20public%20gathered%20at%20a%20%E2%80%98Street%20Reopening%E2%80%99.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20lot%20of%20spaces%20where%20women%20felt%20unsafe%20had%20street%20lights%20that%20were%20broken.%20The%20men%20would%20get%20drunk%2C%20throw%20a%20stone%2C%20and%20break%20the%20street%20light.%20During%20the%20street%20reopening%20functions%2C%20we%20would%20get%20somebody%20from%20BESCOM%20to%20climb%20up%20and%20change%20the%20