neurial-households-2-1728368718-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurial-households-2-1728368718-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-369072%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBy%20integrating%20UPI%20into%20his%20business%20operations%2C%20Ishwargowda%20Basavanagowda%20Patil%20is%20able%20to%20carry%20out%20seamless%20operations%20at%20his%20%3Cem%3Ekirana%3C%2Fem%3E%20shop%20in%20Hubbali%2C%20Karnataka%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStories%20like%20Ishwargowda%E2%80%99s%20provide%20validation%20to%20former%20banker%20and%20SarvaGram%20co-founder%2C%20Utpal%20Isser.%20He%20explains%20how%20the%20success%20of%20rural%20households%20illustrates%20the%20immense%20potential%20they%20hold.%20The%20inspiration%20to%20start%20a%20business%20that%20focussed%20on%20tipping%20the%20scales%20in%20favour%20of%20such%20homes%2C%20struck%20Utpal%20while%20leading%20the%20rural%20and%20inclusive%20banking%20division%20at%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20largest%20private%20sector%20banks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20role%20provided%20him%20a%20front-row%20seat%20to%20the%20transformation%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20rural%20ecosystem%20was%20undergoing%2C%20while%20also%20highlighting%20the%20limitations%20of%20formal%20banking%20institutions%20and%20systems%20that%20weren%E2%80%99t%20conducive%20to%20their%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWatching%20this%20upward%20mobility%20and%20shift%20in%20infrastructure%20(both%20public%20and%20digital)%20motivated%20us%20to%20look%20for%20a%20business%20model%20that%20would%20take%20care%20of%20the%20realities%20of%20these%20%5Brural%5D%20markets.%20We%20intended%20to%20target%20underbanked%20but%20creditworthy%20homes%2C%E2%80%9D%20Utpal%20notes.%20Together%20with%20Sameer%20Mishra%2C%20who%20has%20over%2020%20years%20of%20experience%20in%20rural%20finance%2C%20he%20founded%20SarvaGram%20%E2%80%94%20which%20has%20changed%20many%20lives%20like%20Ishwargowda%E2%80%99s%20with%20access%20to%20credit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20%5BSarvaGram%5D%20isn%E2%80%99t%20an%20overnight%20dream%2C%20but%20instead%2C%20a%20continuing%20success%20story%2C%E2%80%9D%20Utpal%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGiving%20rural%20households%20agency%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Ishwargowda%E2%80%99s%20creditworthiness%20were%20to%20be%20assessed%20solely%20based%20on%20his%20income%20at%20the%20time%2C%20or%20his%20discretionary%20expenses%2C%20he%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20made%20the%20cut.%20A%20lack%20of%20steady%20income%20was%20why%20he%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20considered%20for%20a%20formal%20bank%20loan.%20To%20this%20end%2C%20when%20Utpal%20set%20out%20to%20conceive%20SarvaGram%2C%20he%20was%20keen%20to%20build%20it%20with%20a%20growth-oriented%20ethos%20that%20would%20provide%20loans%20to%20those%20with%20variable%20incomes%2C%20but%20aspirational%20mindsets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20as%20%E2%80%9CIndia%E2%80%99s%20first%20household-centric%2C%20data-led%2C%20%E2%80%98high-tech%20high-touch%E2%80%99%20distribution%20platform%E2%80%9D%2C%20SarvaGram%20is%20extending%20a%20hand%20towards%20rural%20India%20through%20its%20bouquet%20of%20financial%20and%20productivity-enhancing%20offerings.%20The%20cornerstone%20of%20the%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20services%20has%20been%20a%20keen%20focus%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9Cunderbanked%20but%20creditworthy%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FUyhbciwOdQ8%3Fsi%3DJKgdl5rOGHAG-GMb%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPutting%20this%20into%20perspective%2C%20Utpal%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20decided%20to%20focus%20on%20mid-income%20households%20that%20may%20not%20necessarily%20have%20banking%20records%20or%20credit%20track%20records%20to%20prove%20their%20creditworthiness.%20Instead%2C%20their%20creditworthiness%20is%20determined%20by%20their%20%E2%80%98intent%20to%20repay%E2%80%99.%20These%20are%20not%20data-dark%20households%20anymore.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20ripples%20of%20SarvaGram%20are%20currently%20reaching%20over%2016%2C000%20villages%20across%20India%2C%20making%20it%20the%20gold%20standard%20in%20how%20tech%20can%20be%20leveraged%20to%20scale%20the%20dreams%20of%20households%20that%20once%20did%20not%20come%20under%20the%20purview%20of%20formal%20banking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Ishwargowda%20is%20reaping%20the%20benefits%20of%20his%20association%20with%20SarvaGram%20at%20his%20%3Cem%3Ekirana%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ea%20few%20kilometres%20away%2C%20farmer%20Hanumanthappa%20Lingappa%E2%80%99s%20fate%20mirrors%20the%20same%20success.%20It%20will%20be%20a%20decade%20now%20since%20the%20farmer%20has%20been%20cultivating%20sugarcane.%20The%20land%20is%20cropping%20well%20%E2%80%94%20as%20suggested%20by%20the%20sweet%20drink%20that%20the%20farmer%20offers%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-1-1727933757.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Farmer%20Hanumanthappa%20Lingappa%20cultivates%20sugarcane%20while%20also%20collecting%20grains%20from%20neighbouring%20farmers%20and%20selling%20it%20to%20the%20Farmer%20Producer%20Organisations%20(FPOs)%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-1-1727933757.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-1-1727933757-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.co