etterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-2-1727933914-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-2-1727933914-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-2-1727933914-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-2-1727933914-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-368493%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPravesh%20Sharma%20IAS%20(retired)%20and%20Anil%20Kumar%20SG%20have%20pioneered%20Samunnati%20which%20works%20with%20thousands%20of%20FPOs%20across%20India%20to%20provide%20farmers%20with%20market%20linkages%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20drive%20through%20Hubbali%E2%80%99s%20beautiful%20landscapes%20makes%20one%20privy%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3Emandis%20%3C%2Fem%3E(markets)%20and%20beautiful%20village%20homes%2C%20there%20are%20very%20few%20banks%20in%20sight.%20Pravesh%20explains%20the%20reason%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20parlance%20of%20the%20financial%20world%2C%20banks%20have%20not%20seen%20this%20sector%20as%20an%20attractive%20asset%20class.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20where%20Samunnati%20enters.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20genius%20has%20been%20to%20show%20that%20this%20asset%20class%20can%20be%20a%20rewarding%20one%2C%20provided%20it%20is%20structured%20correctly%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pravesh%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Samunnati%2C%20the%20focus%20is%20on%20smallholder%20farmers%20as%20the%20main%20beneficiaries%3B%20a%20paradigm%20shift%20in%20the%20existing%20economic%20view%20and%20opinions.%20But%20it%20was%20vital%20that%20the%20organisation%20be%20designed%20on%20this%20crux%20for%20Anil%2C%20whose%20two-decade-long%20association%20with%20the%20banking%20sector%20introduced%20him%20to%20the%20woes%20of%20agri-enterprises%20that%20lacked%20access%20to%20credit%20and%20loans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20providing%20smallholder%20farmers%20and%20agri%20enterprises%20access%20to%20markets%2C%20financial%20intermediation%2C%20market%20linkages%20and%20advisory%20services%2C%20Samunnati%20enables%20them%20to%20operate%20at%20a%20higher%20equilibrium.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%20is%20a%20standing%20example%20of%20how%20entrepreneurship%20can%20be%20targeted%20at%20providing%20commercially%20viable%20solutions%20to%20a%20customer%20segment%2C%20which%20is%20often%20misunderstood%2C%20and%20sidelined.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20operational%20results%20are%20a%20nod%20to%20their%20incredible%20work%2C%20Anil%20maintains%20that%20the%20organisation%20has%20a%20larger%20goal%20%E2%80%94%20to%20set%20an%20example.%20%E2%80%9CThrough%20Samunnati%2C%20we%20have%20established%20that%20lending%20to%20farmers%20is%20credible%2C%20sustainable%20and%20scalable.%20Samunnati%20has%20demonstrated%20the%20scalability%20of%20lending%20to%20agriculture%2C%20and%20this%20will%20foster%20a%20lot%20of%20banks%20coming%20into%20the%20sector.%20As%20I%20see%20it%2C%20the%20flow%20of%20credit%20to%20the%20agricultural%20sector%20is%20poised%20to%20take%20a%20big%20leap.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmer%20Mrutunjay%20Shankar%20Salimate%2C%20leader%20of%20Kalmeshwara%20FPO%2C%20which%20has%20benefitted%20from%20its%20association%20with%20Samunnati%2C%20reminisces%20how%20in%202016%20when%20they%20started%2C%20they%20were%20just%20a%20group%20of%2050%20farmers.%20%E2%80%9CNow%20we%20have%20more%20than%201%2C400%20farmers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20The%20association%20with%20Samunnati%20has%20been%20a%20shot%20in%20the%20arm%20for%20the%20FPO%E2%80%99s%20work%20of%20supporting%20farmers%20with%20seeds%2C%20fertilisers%2C%20spray%20pumps%2C%20supply%20chain%20operations%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FAvbGO0-Rux8%3Fsi%3DaYFKg-1D4pcxdTAq%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMrutunjay%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20provided%20us%20with%20market%20linkages%2C%20networking%20with%20institutions%20and%20financial%20support.%20They%20have%20also%20conducted%20activities%20to%20identify%20village-level%20entrepreneurs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarvaGram%20and%20Samunnati%E2%80%99s%20success%20stories%20are%20reflective%20of%20how%20entrepreneurs%20can%20create%20businesses%20that%20address%20the%20growing%20aspirations%20of%20millions%20of%20Entrepreneurial%20Households%3Csup%3ETM%3C%2Fsup%3E%20across%20India%2C%20to%20address%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.enmasse.world%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEPIC%20Opportunity%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EPIC%20Opportunity%20is%20a%20description%20of%20the%20multi-trillion%20dollar%20market%20opportunity%20that%20Entrepreneurial%20Households%20represent.%20For%20investors%2C%20it%20provides%20an%20opportunity%20to%20deploy%20capital%20for%20the%20creation%20of%20large%2C%20formal%20institutions%20addressing%20the%20demands%20of%20Entrepreneurial%20Households%2C%20across%20emerging%20markets.%20This%20burgeoning%20asset%20class%20is%20fast%20proving%20to%20be%20the%20new%20centre%20of%20gravity%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20and%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20economic%20prosperity.%20By%20tapping%20into%20the%20potential%20of%20these%20households%2C%20companies%20like%20SarvaGram%20and%20Samunnati%20are%20leading%20the%20way%20and%20showcasing%20that%20impact%20and%20commercial%20returns%20can%20go%20hand-in-hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20growth%20story%20is%20set%20to%20take%20on%20a%20new%20narrative.%20Proof%20of%20this%20lies%20in%20my%20conversation%20with%20farmer%20Mrutunjay.%20While%20a%20wide%20array%20of%20opportunities%20are%20open%20to%20his%20children%2C%20he%20says%2C%20they%20are%20keen%20on%20following%20in%20his%20footsteps.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20want%20to%20grow%20up%20to%20be%20farmers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELeading%20change%20from%20the%20front%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20landscape%20in%20remote%20areas%20of%20India%20does%20seem%20promising.%20And%20the%20feeling%20continues%20402%20km%20away%2C%20in%20Bengaluru.%20Dreams%20are%20brimming%20at%20the%20Nisarga%20Vidyanikethana%20High%20School%2C%20as%20hundreds%20of%20kids%20who%20study%20at%20the%20school%20share%20their%20aspirations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20get%20into%20sports%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20a%2010-year-old.%20While%20another%20says%20he%20will%20join%20the%20Army.%20Hearing%20these%20innocent%20dreams%20has%20school%20head%20Nandan%20Eshwar%20beaming.%20Since%20its%20inception%2C%20the%20school%20has%20served%20as%20a%20space%20for%20budding%20talent.%20Nandan%2C%20whose%20uncle%20Channakeshava%20built%20the%20school%2C%20has%20always%20admired%20the%20students%E2%80%99%20persistence%20to%20learn%20and%20dream%20big.%20His%20uncle%2C%20he%20says%2C%20would%20be%20thrilled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-3-1727934119.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Nisarga%20Vidyanikethana%20High%20School%20in%20Bengaluru%20is%20giving%20wings%20to%20childrens'%20professional%20dreams%20and%20aspirations%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuplo