%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-6-1727934739.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ishwargowda%20Basavanagowda%20Patil%20has%20a%20thriving%20field%20of%20green%20gram%20that%20he%20cultivates%20once%20he%20has%20wrapped%20up%20his%20kirana%20shop%20operations%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-6-1727934739.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-6-1727934739-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-6-1727934739-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-6-1727934739-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-6-1727934739-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-368501%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIshwargowda%20Basavanagowda%20Patil%20has%20a%20thriving%20field%20of%20green%20gram%20that%20he%20cultivates%20once%20he%20has%20wrapped%20up%20his%20%3Cem%3Ekirana%3C%2Fem%3E%20shop%20operations%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20his%20day%20isn%E2%80%99t%20over%20yet.%20He%20isn%E2%80%99t%20heading%20home%20yet%20%E2%80%93%20the%20vast%20fields%20of%20green%20gram%20await%20him.%20You%20see%2C%20Ishwargowda%20may%20be%20a%20businessman.%20But%2C%20he%20is%20essentially%20a%20farmer%20at%20heart.%20During%20a%20walk%20through%20his%20manicured%20fields%2C%20I%20observe%20how%20the%20land%20seems%20parched.%20But%20the%20arrival%20of%20the%20drizzle%20has%20him%20relieved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20around%20the%20expanse%2C%20I%20notice%20how%